{{!
    @template mod_playercross/inactive_words

    Teacher-only warning listing approved pool words that will never actually be
    drawn into a round (outside the current length range, or containing a character
    the game cannot use), shown on view.php above the game area — not below, so it
    can never end up hidden behind the mobile virtual keyboard, which is
    position: fixed to the viewport's bottom edge and therefore has no reserved
    space of its own for content that would otherwise render after it. Never
    rendered for a student — gated by canmanage in view_page_service.php.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "activewordscount": "5 active words in this game.",
        "inactivewordstitle": "Inactive words in this game:",
        "haslengthissues": true,
        "lengthissuestext": "Outside the current length range (2): iluminismo, revolucao.",
        "hascharsetissues": true,
        "charsetissuestext": "Contains a character the game cannot use (1): café-com-leite."
    }
}}
<div class="mod-playercross-inactive-words alert alert-warning mt-3">
    <p class="mb-1"><strong>{{activewordscount}}</strong></p>
    <p class="mb-1"><strong>{{inactivewordstitle}}</strong></p>
    <ul class="mb-0">
        {{#haslengthissues}}
            <li>{{lengthissuestext}}</li>
        {{/haslengthissues}}
        {{#hascharsetissues}}
            <li>{{charsetissuestext}}</li>
        {{/hascharsetissues}}
    </ul>
</div>
